name: AI Nude Portrait #7 frame 179 sold for 70.4 ETH on Tue May 04 2021
description: In 2018 SuperRare and Christie's partnered with Jason Bailey and enlisted Robbie Barrat to create “AI Generated Nude Portrait #7”, which he intended as 300 separate frames of a single artwork. A small handful of these original NFTs are known to still exist. We’ll call them “Robbies”. On May 4th, 2021, frame 179 sold for 70.4ETH ($210K). Generative sales by @dblockdotorg.
